      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-zos-dcp-opn-000  thru det-zos-dcp-opn-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura tipo ordinamento da filtro di selezione *
      *              * ed ordinamento per file [dcp]                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "TO"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      rr-fso-dcp-alf       to   f-key                  .
           perform   det-zos-dcp-cll-000  thru det-zos-dcp-cll-999    .
      *
           if        f-sts                =    "01"
                     move  01             to   w-tip-ord-tip-ord
           else if   f-sts                =    "02"
                     move  02             to   w-tip-ord-tip-ord
           else if   f-sts                =    "03"
                     move  03             to   w-tip-ord-tip-ord
           else if   f-sts                =    "04"
                     move  04             to   w-tip-ord-tip-ord
           else      move  01             to   w-tip-ord-tip-ord      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Open modulo di determinazione buffer dei fabbi- *
      *              * sogni/disponibilita'                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-buf-fod-opn-000  thru det-buf-fod-opn-999    .
